{"word":"εἰσδέρκομαι","slug":"εἰσδέρκομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>εἰσδέρκομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>, with aor2 <a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <el>-έδρᾰκον</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>εἰσδέδροκα</el>) </el><p/><i>to look at</i> or <i>upon</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/>"}]}